TextArea_SetColour
#include Style
#Background wimp 1
Module:	<Window=>window/m>
#Line
#Wrap off
Veneer:	<textarea_set_colour>
Syntax:	TextArea_SetColour
#indent

On Entry:
#indent 6
{FCode}r0 = flags
r1 = window object Id
r2 = 0x4018 + 9 (16417)
r3 = gadget component Id
r4 = foreground
r5 = background
{f}
#indent
On exit:
#indent 6
{FCode}r1-r9 preserved
{f}
#indent
#Wrap
Purpose:	Method sets the colour in the TextArea.